Hi Sudhir,

Are you free now? I am available until 10 AM EST. If not, are you available tomorrow any time between 9 AM - 12 PM EST?

Could you also check if "Advanced Printer and MTP Scanning:" is enabled under "Device Control > Global Settings > File Tracing and Shadowing"? (This setting can also be applied at the group or individual user/computer level). If so, I'd recommend disabling it during the upgrading process.

Thanks!
Andrew
